criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Fmale aged 18- 45;

          2. Meet Rotterdam criteria(2003);

          3. body mass index (BMI)≥30 kg/m2

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Gender is male;

          2. Younger than 18 years old or older than 45 years old ;

          3. secondary obesity due to endocrine disorders;

          4. history of malignant tumors; 5）sever hepatic and renal disease;

        6) concurrent participation in other clinical trials; 7) sever endocrine and hereditary
        diseases; 8) mental illnesses that rendered them unable to provide informed consent; 9)
        patients declining to undergo complete study testing.
